          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Zr targets were prepared by electron beam evaporation",
                "of natural isotopic composition metallic Zr onto",
                "6.5 um thick Al foil backings and range between",
                " (0.8-1.5)xE18 Zr atoms/cm2 with an uncertainty of 5%."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The cross section was measured in the proton",
                "energy range between 1450 and 2800 keV covering",
                "completely the Gamow window for 91Zr(p,g)92Nb."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SITA"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " In most cases two targets, placed behind each",
                "other were irradiated in a single activation in order",
                "to reduce the beam time requirement and referred to as",
                "front and rear targets. Targets were irradiated with a",
                "proton beam for 5 to 48 hours.",
                "Beam intensity was 4 - 5 uA."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GSPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Activity measurement of the reaction products",
                "was done by Gamma-spectrometry based on HPGe detectors."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "EN-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                "The uncertainty on the median energy in the",
                "target includes cumulative effects of uncertainty of",
                "incident beam energy, uncertainty of energy loss of",
                "each foil due to thickness variation and straggling",
                "effects. Uncertainty of the primari incident beam",
                "energy was +- 1 keV"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-T",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                "The uncertainty on the cross section values",
                "are estimated in the standard way as the square root",
                "of the quadratic summation of the independently",
                "contributing parameters. Uncertainty of time parameters",
                "is not included."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-1",
